2009-12-30  Jan Moringen  <jan@steed>

	Use `process-put' and `process-get' instead `rudel-set-process-object' 
	and `rudel-process-object'
	* tls/rudel-tls.el (rudel-tls-make-process):
	 (rudel-tls-start-tls):
	 (rudel-tls-wait-init):
