	* obby/rudel-obby-server.el
	 (rudel-obby-client::rudel-obby/obby_document/subscribe): minor
	 rearrangement of expressions
	 (rudel-obby-client::rudel-obby/obby_document/unsubscribe): minor
	 rearrangement of expressions

